name: CSVr
tagline: Manipulate and combine CSVs in R
body:
### Project CSVr
This is my personal project. CSVr aims at making the data pre-processing step less painful when working with multiple CSV/text files.

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```
